00:20:20,916 --> 00:20:23,041
Looks like a simple
case of exhaustion.

257
00:20:23,125 --> 00:20:25,041
As long as her headaches
aren't getting any worse,

258
00:20:25,125 --> 00:20:27,333
I'd say it's
nothing serious.

259
00:20:27,416 --> 00:20:30,083
That may be, Doctor, but
it doesn't change the fact

260
00:20:30,166 --> 00:20:33,250
that we must examine Kagura
as soon as possible.

261
00:20:33,333 --> 00:20:34,333
Saiga...!

262
00:20:34,416 --> 00:20:36,000
Accept Ochiai's
proposal...

263
00:20:36,083 --> 00:20:38,000
I beg you.

264
00:20:38,083 --> 00:20:39,375
Professor...

265
00:20:43,791 --> 00:20:46,833
I don't understand why he's
so reticent to testify!

266
00:20:46,916 --> 00:20:48,708
It's a complicated
decision for him.

267
00:20:48,791 --> 00:20:50,500
He wants to do what's
best for the girl.

268
00:20:50,583 --> 00:20:51,875
But unless
we can get Kagura

269
00:20:51,958 --> 00:20:54,208
moved to the proper
facilities...

270
00:20:54,291 --> 00:20:56,166
she'll die and then
it will be too late.

271
00:20:56,250 --> 00:20:58,000
If we don't get a
living tissue sample...

272
00:20:58,083 --> 00:21:00,333
Nishiya!

273
00:21:00,416 --> 00:21:02,375
While I appreciate your
help getting us in touch

274
00:21:02,458 --> 00:21:05,083
with Representative Ochiai...

275
00:21:05,166 --> 00:21:08,208
I won't allow you to turn
this into a publicity stunt!

276
00:21:27,916 --> 00:21:29,666
Miss Kagura...

277
00:21:32,916 --> 00:21:34,625
I have something very
important to tell you,

278
00:21:34,708 --> 00:21:36,208
about your health...

279
00:21:36,291 --> 00:21:39,250
Your friends have
been keeping secrets.

280
00:21:39,333 --> 00:21:41,416
You have to appear
before the legislature.

281
00:21:41,500 --> 00:21:43,750
If we delay a full examination
of you for much longer,

282
00:21:43,833 --> 00:21:46,000
Your condition
will kill you.

283
00:21:46,083 --> 00:21:48,000
And your friend,
Mister Saiga...

284
00:21:48,083 --> 00:21:50,666
will be left
permanently blind.

285
00:23:32,208 --> 00:23:36,500
In this city, insanity
runs silent but deep.

286
00:23:36,583 --> 00:23:39,958
Is a lie still a lie if it's
for your own good?

287
00:23:40,041 --> 00:23:41,958
Will the man
be a friend?

288
00:23:42,041 --> 00:23:44,791
Or will
he cut and run?

